Package org.flowable.cmmn.api.repository

Interface CmmnDeploymentBuilder

public interface CmmnDeploymentBuilder
Builder for creating new deployments, similar to the bpmn deployment builder. A builder instance can be obtained through CmmnRepositoryService.createDeployment(). Multiple resources can be added to one deployment before calling the deploy() operation. After deploying, no more changes can be made to the returned deployment and the builder instance can be disposed.
Author:
Tijs Rademakers, Joram Barrez
